Article.ArticleTitle: A new isoflavanone from Ficus tikoua Bur.

AbstractText: A new isoflavanone compound, ficustikounone A (1), together with 22 known flavones, was isolated from Ficus tikoua Bur. The structures of these isolates were determined by UV, ECD, HRESIMS, 1D and 2D spectral analyses.
